original_title: The Devil Down Under: Satanic Panic in Australia from Rosaleen Norton to Alison's Birthday
overview: A video essay about satanic panic in Australia from Rosaleen Norton to Alison's birthday,based on Alexandra Heller- Nicholas's chapter of the same name from the book "Satanic Panic : pop cultural Paronia in the 1980s".
title: The Devil Down Under: Satanic Panic in Australia from Rosaleen Norton to Alison's Birthday
